Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&}（深呼吸）{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&}わ… 私は⸺{\c}
